# ── About ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

msgid "Nuestra Filosofía"
msgstr "Our Philosophy"

msgid "Minimalismo"
msgstr "Minimalism"

msgid "sin compromiso"
msgstr "without compromise"

msgid "Minimalismo sin compromiso"
msgstr "Uncompromising minimalism"

msgid ""
"En <strong>UNLABELED</strong>, creemos que la prenda debe hablar por sí "
"misma. Vivimos en la intersección del arte, la música alternativa y la "
"libertad absoluta."
msgstr ""
"At <strong>UNLABELED</strong>, we believe the garment should speak for "
"itself. We live at the intersection of art, alternative music, and "
"absolute freedom."

msgid ""
"\"La identidad no se define por una marca, sino por la calidad de lo que "
"eliges vestir.\""
msgstr ""
"\"Identity is not defined by a brand, but by the quality of what you "
"choose to wear.\""

msgid ""
"Nuestras colecciones son curadas detalladamente para ofrecer piezas "
"atemporales, sin logos visibles, enfocándonos únicamente en la manufactura y "
"los materiales premium."
msgstr ""
"Our collections are carefully curated to offer timeless pieces, with "
"no visible logos, focusing solely on manufacturing and premium materials."

msgid "Calidad"
msgstr "Quality"

msgid "Atemporalidad"
msgstr "Timelessness"

msgid "Sin Logos"
msgstr "No Logos"

msgid "Manufactura"
msgstr "Manufacturing"

msgid "Materiales seleccionados de primera calidad."
msgstr "Selected first-class materials."

msgid "Piezas que trascienden tendencias efímeras."
msgstr "Pieces that transcend fleeting trends."

msgid "La prenda habla, no la etiqueta."
msgstr "The garment speaks, not the label."

msgid "Control detallado en cada proceso."
msgstr "Detailed control in every process."

